# type

**Instance Property**

The kind of the underlying value that the data value wraps.

## Declaration

```swift
var type: MLDataValue.ValueType { get }
```

## Inspecting the type

- **MLDataValue.ValueType**: An enumeration describing the supported underlying types that an `MLDataValue wraps`.
